WEBVTT

00:00.768 --> 00:02.570
MAX, HONEY, HELP ME ZIP UP
MY WEDDING DRESS.

00:03.471 --> 00:05.206
WHY ARE YOU
TRYING IT ON NOW?

00:05.206 --> 00:07.808
YOU AND DAD AREN'T RENEWING
YOUR VOWS FOR ANOTHER MONTH.

00:07.808 --> 00:09.677
I'M TRYING IT ON ONCE A WEEK

00:09.677 --> 00:13.281
TO REMIND MYSELF NOT TO EAT
ANYTHING THAT TASTES GOOD.

00:15.849 --> 00:18.386
BREAKFAST TASTED
REAL GOOD.

00:19.853 --> 00:23.724
NOW, TRY THIS ON SO I CAN SEE
IF THE FLOWERS ARE EVEN.

00:33.367 --> 00:35.303
ALL RIGHT,
I GET THE MESSAGE.

00:35.303 --> 00:37.171
WE'LL SPEND
MORE TIME TOGETHER.

00:37.171 --> 00:40.040
MOM PUT IT ON ME.

00:41.409 --> 00:44.778
I THOUGHT YOU LEFT
FOR WORK.

00:44.778 --> 00:46.714
I FORGOT SOME FILES.

00:46.714 --> 00:48.649
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING BACK THERE?

00:48.649 --> 00:50.984
I DON'T WANT YOU TO SEE ME
IN MY WEDDING DRESS.

00:50.984 --> 00:52.320
COME ON, ANGIE,
LET ME SEE.

00:52.320 --> 00:54.755
NO, STOP IT.
IT'S BAD LUCK.

00:54.755 --> 00:57.858
FINE. IF YOU'RE NOT LEAVING,
I'M TAKING IT OFF.

00:57.858 --> 00:59.593
THAT'LL SHOW ME.

00:59.593 --> 01:01.629
HEY, KIDS,
STAY IN YOUR ROOMS!

01:01.629 --> 01:04.665
YOUR MOM'S GONNA TEACH ME
A LESSON. [ WHISTLES ]

01:09.069 --> 01:10.738
GEORGE, LET'S GO.

01:10.738 --> 01:12.072
OH, OH, OH.

01:14.041 --> 01:15.443
ERNIE!

01:15.443 --> 01:17.911
OH, I'M SORRY, ANGIE.

01:17.911 --> 01:19.647
I DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING...

01:19.647 --> 01:22.350
THAT I'M GONNA REMEMBER
THE REST OF MY LIFE.

01:22.350 --> 01:23.651
IT'S ALL RIGHT, DUDE.
IT HAPPENS.

01:23.651 --> 01:25.486
SOMEDAY YOU'RE
GOING TO GET MARRIED.

01:25.486 --> 01:27.020
I'M GONNA LOOK
AT YOUR WIFE NAKED.

01:27.020 --> 01:28.822
GO AHEAD AND DO IT, GEORGE,

01:28.822 --> 01:33.861
BUT MINE'S NOT GONNA LOOK
ANYTHING LIKE THAT.

01:33.861 --> 01:36.730
MOM? PHONE.

01:36.730 --> 01:40.201
DAD, I NEED A RIDE TO ALLENDALE
SO I CAN REGISTER.

01:40.201 --> 01:42.803
CAN'T I JUST WRITE
A CHECK FOR THE $14,000,

01:42.803 --> 01:45.639
THEN GO IN THE GARAGE AND
CRY LIKE I DID LAST YEAR?

01:45.639 --> 01:48.409
NO, I MISSED REGULAR
REGISTRATION WHEN I RAN AWAY,

01:48.409 --> 01:50.344
SO YOU AND MOM HAVE
TO BACK ME UP

01:50.344 --> 01:51.879
WHEN I TELL THEM
I WAS SICK.

01:51.879 --> 01:55.283
YOU KNOW, CARMEN, WE LIE
TO EACH OTHER ALL THE TIME,

01:55.283 --> 01:58.886
BUT LYING TOGETHER
AS A FAMILY...

01:58.886 --> 02:01.121
THAT'S NICE.

02:03.991 --> 02:05.526
WHY AREN'T YOU HIDING?

02:05.526 --> 02:08.061
I THOUGHT I WASN'T SUPPOSED
TO SEE YOU IN THE DRESS.

02:08.061 --> 02:09.229
IT DOESN'T MATTER NOW.

02:09.229 --> 02:10.764
LaMARIE WENT UNDER.

02:10.764 --> 02:13.100
I JUST LOST MY JOB.

02:13.100 --> 02:15.803
BABY, I'M SORRY.

02:15.803 --> 02:17.405
WHAT AM I GONNA DO?

02:17.405 --> 02:19.740
YOU'LL FIND
ANOTHER JOB, HUH?

02:19.740 --> 02:23.477
I'VE BEEN THERE.
I'VE BEEN OUT OF WORK.

02:23.477 --> 02:26.547
REMEMBER WE HAD TO ALMOST
CARMEN'S QUINCENERA?

02:26.547 --> 02:29.283
WHAT DO YOU SAY TO ME EVERY TIME
I HAVE A BIG SETBACK?

02:29.283 --> 02:30.651
A DOOR MAY HAVE CLOSED,

02:30.651 --> 02:34.255
BUT A WINDOW'S
JUST OPENED WITH SUNLIGHT.

02:34.255 --> 02:36.924
AM I REALLY THAT ANNOYING?

02:36.924 --> 02:39.693
LET'S NOT GO THERE
WHILE YOU'RE DOWN.

02:39.693 --> 02:41.329
LOOK, ANGIE...

02:41.329 --> 02:44.232
YOU'RE YOUNG, YOU'RE SMART,
YOU'RE GETTING MARRIED --

02:44.232 --> 02:46.267
YOU'VE GOT
YOUR WHOLE LIFE AHEAD OF YOU.

02:46.267 --> 02:48.802
WE CAN'T RENEW OUR VOWS NOW.

02:48.802 --> 02:54.608
WE SHOULD POSTPONE THE WEDDING
UNTIL I GET ANOTHER JOB.

02:54.608 --> 02:58.312
YOU SAW ME IN MY DRESS
BEFORE I HID, DIDN'T YOU?

02:58.312 --> 03:00.681
THAT'S WHEN
THE BAD LUCK STARTED.

03:00.681 --> 03:03.217
YEAH, I RUINED
OUR RUN OF GOOD LUCK --

03:03.217 --> 03:05.786
WITH OUR DYSLEXIC SON,
OUR RUNAWAY DAUGHTER,

03:05.786 --> 03:07.888
AND MY MOTHER
WHO SHOWS NO SIGN

03:07.888 --> 03:11.992
OF AGING OR DISEASE
WHATSOEVER.

03:11.992 --> 03:16.697
[ COUGHING ]

03:16.697 --> 03:18.065
HOLY COW.

03:18.065 --> 03:20.468
WHERE DID THAT COME FROM?

03:20.468 --> 03:22.936
ANGIE, I SEE
A WINDOW OPENING.

03:22.936 --> 03:25.339
[ BENNY COUGHING ]

03:25.339 --> 03:28.942
IT'S GETTING WIDER.

03:28.942 --> 03:31.679
[ INTRO TO WAR'S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

03:35.483 --> 03:40.854
* ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER *

03:54.768 --> 03:56.970
OH, HI,
ASSISTANT PRINCIPAL CAPLAN?

03:56.970 --> 03:59.473
WE'RE HERE TO REGISTER
CARMEN FOR THE YEAR.

03:59.473 --> 04:02.510
OH, RIGHT.
LET ME GRAB YOUR FILE.

04:05.145 --> 04:06.347
OHH.

04:06.347 --> 04:07.648
HMM.

04:07.648 --> 04:09.283
YOU NEED TO TALK
TO PRINCIPAL BORDEN.

04:09.283 --> 04:10.751
SHE'LL BE
BACK ON FRIDAY.

04:10.751 --> 04:12.920
WAIT. TALK ABOUT WHAT?
WHAT'S IN THAT FILE?

04:12.920 --> 04:14.288
IS SOMETHING WRONG?

04:14.288 --> 04:17.458
YES, BUT I'M NOT
ALLOWED TO TELL YOU.

04:17.458 --> 04:20.594
WHY NOT?
YOU'RE THE ASSISTANT PRINCIPAL.

04:20.594 --> 04:22.095
APPARENTLY I DON'T HAVE
THE PEOPLE SKILLS

04:22.095 --> 04:23.631
IT WOULD TAKE TO TELL YOU

04:23.631 --> 04:25.866
THAT YOUR DAUGHTER'S
BEEN KICKED OUT OF ALLENDALE.

04:25.866 --> 04:28.602
OH, THERE I GO
BEING ALL ABRUPT AGAIN.

04:29.837 --> 04:31.505
THIS HAS GOT TO BE
A MISTAKE.

04:31.505 --> 04:33.441
SINCE THE CAT'S
OUT OF THE BAG...

04:33.441 --> 04:36.510
UNIFORM VIOLATIONS -- SIX,
TARDIES -- EIGHT,

04:36.510 --> 04:39.513
PUBLIC DISPLAYS
OF AFFECTION -- 32.

04:39.513 --> 04:41.515
WELL, THAT CAN BE EXPLAINED.

04:41.515 --> 04:43.717
SHE USED TO DATE
JASON MacNAMARA.

04:43.717 --> 04:46.387
HE'S VERY HOT.

04:46.387 --> 04:48.922
QUARTERBACK,
BROWN HAIR, SEA-FOAM EYES.

04:48.922 --> 04:50.290
DAD!

04:50.290 --> 04:53.561
YOU GOT TO LOOK CLOSE, CARMEN,
OTHERWISE THEY JUST LOOK GREEN.

04:55.195 --> 04:57.498
LISTEN, JANET,
YOU CANNOT PUNISH CARMEN

04:57.498 --> 04:59.967
JUST BECAUSE SHE GOT SICK
AND MISSED HER FINALS.

04:59.967 --> 05:01.234
DID SHE CATCH A COLD

05:01.234 --> 05:04.037
WHEN SHE RAN OFF TO
SAN FRANCISCO WITH HER BOYFRIEND

05:04.037 --> 05:05.439
AND HUNG OUT WITH RAPPERS?

05:05.439 --> 05:07.941
YOU KNOW WHAT?
THIS IS INSULTING.

05:07.941 --> 05:10.378
MY DAUGHTER WAS SICK,
END OF THE STORY.

05:10.378 --> 05:14.047
HAVE YOU SEEN THIS RUNAWAY?

05:14.047 --> 05:16.249
OKAY, HERE'S THE TRUTH.

05:16.249 --> 05:20.988
AND IT'S HARD
FOR A PARENT TO SAY...

05:20.988 --> 05:23.657
BUT MY LAMB RAN AWAY...

05:25.459 --> 05:29.397
BECAUSE SHE HAS DEEP
EMOTIONAL SCARS INTERNALLY.

05:29.397 --> 05:31.432
[ Voice breaking ]
IT'S NO REASON

05:31.432 --> 05:33.467
TO KICK HER OUT OF SCHOOL.

05:34.935 --> 05:37.738
THERE'S SOMETHING ELSE
IN THAT FILE, ISN'T THERE?

05:37.738 --> 05:39.707
SHE APPEARED
IN A CHINGY VIDEO

05:39.707 --> 05:41.709
HAVING A PILLOW FIGHT
ON A WATERBED.

05:41.709 --> 05:44.445
I DIDN'T GET CUT OUT!
[ LAUGHS ]

05:44.445 --> 05:48.015
OKAY, STAND BEHIND ME, AND,
shh!

05:49.617 --> 05:53.587
MR. AND MRS. LOPEZ, WE HAVE
A LONG WAITING LIST OF STUDENTS

05:53.587 --> 05:56.657
WHO DON'T LIE, RUN AWAY,
AND MISS THEIR FINALS.

05:56.657 --> 05:59.159
I THINK WE CAN ALL PROBABLY
AGREE THAT CARMEN AND ALLENDALE

05:59.159 --> 06:00.461
ARE NOT SUCH A GREAT MATCH.

06:00.461 --> 06:02.430
PERHAPS YOU SHOULD TRY
PUBLIC SCHOOL AGAIN.

06:02.430 --> 06:04.565
NO. UH, NO.

06:04.565 --> 06:07.300
I -- I CAN'T GO BACK
TO PUBLIC SCHOOL.

06:07.300 --> 06:10.471
THEY CALLED ME A WHORE.

06:10.471 --> 06:14.307
BEFORE YOU MADE THE VIDEO?

06:14.307 --> 06:15.543
YOU KNOW WHAT?
FORGET IT.

06:15.543 --> 06:17.244
WE DON'T NEED
THIS SCHOOL.

06:17.244 --> 06:18.612
MAY I SUGGEST ST. THERESA'S?

06:18.612 --> 06:21.615
THEY TAKE THE HARD CASES,
AND THEY STILL HIT.

06:21.615 --> 06:24.317
NO. DAD, NO WAY.

06:24.317 --> 06:27.621
THAT'S AN ALL-GIRLS SCHOOL.
YOU KNOW HOW GIRLS HATE ME.

06:27.621 --> 06:30.424
CARMEN, YOU JUST GOT FORCED
OUT OF PUBLIC SCHOOL.

06:30.424 --> 06:32.292
YOU GOT KICKED OUT
OF PRIVATE SCHOOL.

06:32.292 --> 06:33.627
YOU'RE RUNNING OUT
OF OPTIONS.

06:33.627 --> 06:35.328
I CAN'T GO
TO CATHOLIC SCHOOL.

06:35.328 --> 06:36.464
WHAT'S LEFT?

06:36.464 --> 06:38.599
HOMESCHOOLING.

06:38.599 --> 06:39.833
MOM COULD TEACH ME.

06:39.833 --> 06:41.902
WHY SHOULD YOUR MOM
BE PUNISHED?

06:43.737 --> 06:47.374
GEORGE, I DO HAVE TIME NOW
SINCE I'M NOT WORKING,

06:47.374 --> 06:49.543
AND THIS IS A CRUCIAL YEAR
FOR CARMEN

06:49.543 --> 06:51.545
IF SHE WANTS
TO GET INTO COLLEGE.

06:51.545 --> 06:53.714
HOMESCHOOLING --
THAT'S A BIG COMMITMENT.

06:53.714 --> 06:56.517
YOU KNOW THAT SPECIAL MOMENT
EVERY MORNING

06:56.517 --> 06:58.619
WHEN CARMEN FINALLY
LEAVES FOR SCHOOL,

06:58.619 --> 07:02.089
AND YOU SAY,
"THANK GOD, SHE'S GONE!"

07:03.423 --> 07:04.692
DAD....

07:04.692 --> 07:07.561
I PROMISE I'LL WORK
REALLY, REALLY HARD.

07:07.561 --> 07:08.596
YOU'VE SAID
THAT BEFORE.

07:08.596 --> 07:10.363
IT'D SAVE US $14,000.

07:10.363 --> 07:12.600
WELL, IF IT'S THAT IMPORTANT
TO THE BOTH OF YOU...

07:12.600 --> 07:15.335
HEY, GUESS WHAT.

07:15.335 --> 07:16.737
MY DAUGHTER'S
JUST BEEN ACCEPTED

07:16.737 --> 07:18.506
TO THE MOST EXCLUSIVE SCHOOL
IN L.A.

07:18.506 --> 07:19.973
THAT'S RIGHT.

07:19.973 --> 07:22.610
LOPEZ HIGH...

07:22.610 --> 07:24.678
COUNTRY DAY ACADEMY.

07:24.678 --> 07:27.515
MY DAUGHTER'S GONNA BE
THE CLASS PRESIDENT,

07:27.515 --> 07:29.216
VALEDICTORIAN, PROM QUEEN --

07:29.216 --> 07:32.152
ALL THE THINGS SHE CAN'T BE
WITH THOSE OTHER KIDS AROUND.

07:43.597 --> 07:44.498
WOW, YOU'VE BEEN BUSY.

07:45.432 --> 07:47.267
I GOT A START-UP KIT
ON THE INTERNET.

07:47.267 --> 07:48.602
THIS IS ALL THE COURSE WORK

07:48.602 --> 07:50.103
THAT CARMEN NEEDS
FOR HER JUNIOR YEAR.

07:50.103 --> 07:52.105
AND I'M IN
AN ONLINE BIDDING WAR

07:52.105 --> 07:55.809
WITH A MORMON MOTHER OF SEVEN
FOR AN OVERHEAD PROJECTOR.

07:58.045 --> 08:00.681
WOW, IT'S STARTING TO LOOK
LIKE A REAL SCHOOL IN HERE.

08:00.681 --> 08:02.482
ALL YOU NEED
IS A BULLY OUTSIDE SMOKING --

08:02.482 --> 08:04.017
HERE HE COMES.

08:07.721 --> 08:10.090
COME ON.
WE'RE GONNA BE LATE.

08:10.090 --> 08:12.726
HEY, WHAT
IS ALL THIS STUFF?

08:12.726 --> 08:14.595
ANGIE'S HOMESCHOOLING
CARMEN, MOM.

08:14.595 --> 08:16.129
OH.

08:16.129 --> 08:18.599
SO THE OUT-OF-WORK
MAKEUP SALESWOMAN

08:18.599 --> 08:20.233
IS GONNA TEACH
YOUR DAUGHTER?

08:20.233 --> 08:23.003
AT LEAST SHE'S PART
OF HER KID'S EDUCATION.

08:23.003 --> 08:25.338
YOU WOULDN'T EVEN HELP ME
WITH MY HOMEWORK.

08:25.338 --> 08:30.277
THAT'S BECAUSE IT TOOK FOREVER
FOR YOU TO READ ONE PAGE.

08:30.277 --> 08:33.046
I WAS DYSLEXIC!

08:33.046 --> 08:36.015
EXCUSES.

08:36.015 --> 08:39.219
GEORGE, I DID
THE ALPHABET BACKWARDS

08:39.219 --> 08:42.556
WITH THE COP'S FLASHLIGHT
IN MY EYES.

08:42.556 --> 08:44.457
AND YOU COULD NOT EVEN
FIGURE OUT

08:44.457 --> 08:46.326
THAT FROG AND TOAD
WERE FRIENDS.

08:46.326 --> 08:47.260
JEEZ!

08:48.996 --> 08:52.299
CARMEN,
YOU JUST MADE IT.

08:52.299 --> 08:53.801
[ RINGING ]

08:53.801 --> 08:56.770
HAVE A SEAT.
IT'S TIME TO START SCHOOL.

08:56.770 --> 08:58.038
OH, COME ON, MOM.

08:58.038 --> 09:00.040
WE DON'T NEED
TO START THIS EARLY.

09:00.040 --> 09:02.109
MOST TEACHERS
HAVE 30 STUDENTS,

09:02.109 --> 09:04.477
AND THAT MEANS WE ONLY NEED
1/30 OF A NORMAL SCHOOL DAY.

09:04.477 --> 09:07.881
YOU CAN TEACH ME HOW TO FIGURE
THAT OUT AFTER LUNCH. BYE-BYE.

09:07.881 --> 09:10.250
AH, AH, AH.
CARMEN.

09:10.250 --> 09:12.185
WHEN I RING THIS BELL...

09:12.185 --> 09:13.654
[ RINGING ]

09:13.654 --> 09:15.422
...I AM NOT YOUR MOM.

09:15.422 --> 09:16.657
I AM YOUR TEACHER.

09:16.657 --> 09:18.091
NOW SIT DOWN.

09:18.091 --> 09:20.661
OKAY.

09:20.661 --> 09:22.796
WE'VE GOT
ENGLISH, HISTORY, LUNCH.

09:22.796 --> 09:24.497
ALGEBRA II, CHEMISTRY --

09:24.497 --> 09:27.334
THEN IF THE DELIVERY GUY GETS
HERE WITH OUR PLASTIC FLUTES --

09:27.334 --> 09:29.236
MUSIC CLASS.

09:29.236 --> 09:31.038
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

09:31.038 --> 09:32.840
THIS IS GONNA BE
LIKE REAL SCHOOL.

09:32.840 --> 09:35.075
WELL, UH,
IF YOU DON'T LIKE IT,

09:35.075 --> 09:37.811
THERE'S ALWAYS
ST. THERESA'S.

09:44.151 --> 09:47.220
WE'VE BEEN WAITING
FOR YOU, MY CHILD.

09:47.220 --> 09:50.090
WA-CHA!

09:50.090 --> 09:51.759
WELL, I'M OFF
TO REAL SCHOOL,

09:51.759 --> 09:53.761
WHERE NO ONE
CAN FORCE ME TO LEARN.

09:53.761 --> 09:55.062
SEE YOU, SUCKER.

09:55.062 --> 09:58.165
HEY, WE CAN HOMESCHOOL
YOU, TOO. HUH?

09:58.165 --> 10:02.335
HOW'D YOU LIKE TO GO THE PROM
IN THE GARAGE WITH YOUR SISTER?

10:05.839 --> 10:07.374
ARE YOU KIDDING?

10:07.374 --> 10:09.609
SHE'S THE KIND OF GIRL
YOU MEET AFTER PROM

10:09.609 --> 10:11.311
WHEN YOU DROP
YOUR REAL DATE OFF.

10:11.311 --> 10:12.245
OHH!

10:21.121 --> 10:23.924
OKAY, I'VE BEEN TEACHING YOU
FOR 2 WEEKS

10:23.924 --> 10:24.858
AT 7 1/2 HOURS A DAY.

10:24.858 --> 10:26.393
IF I TEACH YOU FOR 52 WEEKS,

10:26.393 --> 10:29.162
BY THE END OF THE YEAR,
WHAT WILL YOU HAVE LEARNED?

10:29.162 --> 10:31.164
I'VE LEARNED
THAT GOOD PEOPLE CAN SNAP,

10:31.164 --> 10:33.100
AND CHILDREN SHOULD NOT
BE TRIED AS ADULTS.

10:33.100 --> 10:38.405
MISS LOPEZ, ARE WE BUCKING
FOR A SECOND DETENTION?

10:38.405 --> 10:42.042
NO, MRS. LOPEZ.

10:43.576 --> 10:44.878
CAN DAD JUST TEACH ME NOW?

10:44.878 --> 10:47.347
I REALLY WANT TO KNOW
HOW BUSINESS WORKS.

10:49.416 --> 10:51.318
OKAY, SHE'S YOURS.

10:51.318 --> 10:54.287
BUT AFTER YOUR DAD'S
LUNCH HOUR, I'LL PICK YOU UP,

10:54.287 --> 10:56.857
AND WE CAN CONTINUE
WITH OUR FRENCH LESSON.

10:56.857 --> 10:59.426
[ SPEAKING FRENCH ]

10:59.426 --> 11:01.394
NOW, CLASS...

11:01.394 --> 11:03.296
THE ASSEMBLY LINE
HASN'T CHANGED MUCH

11:03.296 --> 11:05.833
SINCE HENRY FORD FIRST
STARTED TO MASS-PRODUCE --

11:05.833 --> 11:07.134
DAD, I COULD CARE LESS.

11:07.134 --> 11:09.369
I JUST WANTED
TO GET AWAY FROM MOM.

11:09.369 --> 11:10.704
WHAT?

11:10.704 --> 11:12.773
HEY, I SPENT THREE HOURS
ON THE INTERNET

11:12.773 --> 11:14.742
LEARNING ABOUT PRODUCTION,
MANUFACTURING,

11:14.742 --> 11:16.109
AND INDUSTRIAL INNOVATION.

11:16.109 --> 11:18.378
WHAT AM I GONNA DO
WITH THIS CRAP NOW?

11:18.378 --> 11:21.181
DAD, SHE'S DRIVING ME CRAZY.

11:21.181 --> 11:24.084
I MEAN, SHE'S TURNING
EVERYTHING INTO A LESSON.

11:24.084 --> 11:26.419
SHE WOULDN'T EVEN LET ME
USE THE BATHROOM

11:26.419 --> 11:27.955
UNTIL I ASKED HER IN FRENCH.

11:27.955 --> 11:29.723
I ALMOST HAD
A LE PETITE ACCIDENT

11:29.723 --> 11:31.992
RIGHT IN FRONT OF THE FRIDGE!

11:31.992 --> 11:34.194
LOOK, CARMEN,
ARE YOU LEARNING?

11:34.194 --> 11:35.495
YES, BUT --

11:35.495 --> 11:36.663
THAT'S WHAT'S IMPORTANT.

11:36.663 --> 11:39.099
ALL RIGHT,
THIS IS YOUR EDUCATION.

11:39.099 --> 11:41.301
IF YOUR MOM'S GOING
A LITTLE OVERBOARD,

11:41.301 --> 11:43.170
IT'S BECAUSE SHE
JUST LOST HER JOB,

11:43.170 --> 11:44.637
THE WEDDING'S BEEN POSTPONED,

11:44.637 --> 11:46.706
AND SHE'S GOT
NOTHING ELSE TO FOCUS ON.

11:46.706 --> 11:48.208
SO CUT HER SOME SLACK.

11:48.208 --> 11:50.177
THIS MAY COME
AS A SURPRISE TO YOU,

11:50.177 --> 11:52.445
BUT YOUR MOTHER
LOOKS AT YOU CHILDREN

11:52.445 --> 11:53.713
AS HER GREATEST ACHIEVEMENT.

11:53.713 --> 11:55.916
SO, WHAT ARE WE TO YOU?

12:00.220 --> 12:03.323
YOU'RE DEFINITELY
IN THE TOP FIVE.

12:05.158 --> 12:09.229
BUT IF I EVER CHIP ONE IN
FROM THE TRAP, YOU'RE OUT!

12:14.401 --> 12:15.535
[ BELL DINGS ]

12:15.535 --> 12:18.405
PENCILS DOWN.

12:18.405 --> 12:20.407
OKAY, TIME FOR CHEMISTRY.

12:20.407 --> 12:22.042
I'LL MEET YOU IN THE LAB.

12:28.181 --> 12:31.051
GOOD AFTERNOON,
MISS LOPEZ.

12:31.051 --> 12:33.520
TODAY WE'RE STUDYING
CHEMICAL REACTIONS.

12:33.520 --> 12:38.191
I'M DROPPING ANTACID TABLETS
INTO THESE GLASSES OF WATER --

12:38.191 --> 12:40.160
EACH A DIFFERENT TEMPERATURE.

12:42.262 --> 12:44.865
YOU CAN'T DRINK
THE EXPERIMENT.

12:44.865 --> 12:46.566
I'M SORRY,
BUT MY STOMACH HURTS

12:46.566 --> 12:49.436
BECAUSE THE LUNCH LADY
MADE CRAPPY MEATLOAF.

12:51.805 --> 12:53.540
THAT'S IT.
POP QUIZ.

12:53.540 --> 12:57.811
NAME ELEMENTS 1 THROUGH 20
ON THE PERIODIC TABLE

12:57.811 --> 12:58.912
ACCORDING TO WEIGHT.

12:58.912 --> 13:00.280
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

13:00.280 --> 13:03.150
TELL IT TO THE CHICKEN.
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

13:07.787 --> 13:10.423
HEY, HOW'D
THE HOMESCHOOLING GO TODAY?

13:10.423 --> 13:11.558
HORRIBLE.

13:11.558 --> 13:13.160
I'M NOT GONNA LIE.

13:13.160 --> 13:15.595
I HAD TWO GLASSES OF CHARDONNAY
WHILE SHE WAS TAKING A TEST.

13:15.595 --> 13:18.398
THAT'S THE ONLY REASON
SHE'S NOT DEAD.

13:18.398 --> 13:20.300
MAYBE YOU NEED
A LITTLE BREAK.

13:20.300 --> 13:23.837
I COULD GIVE CARMEN
AN AUTO-SHOP LESSON AT MY HOUSE.

13:23.837 --> 13:26.206
MOM, YOU'RE NOT GOING
TO USE CARMEN

13:26.206 --> 13:29.142
TO SIPHON GAS OUT
OF THE NEIGHBOR'S CAR AGAIN.

13:29.142 --> 13:31.845
THE GARCIAS
HAVE A BIG R.V.

13:31.845 --> 13:33.480
THEY NEVER GO ANYWHERE.

13:33.480 --> 13:36.516
THAT'S 'CAUSE
THEY DON'T HAVE THE GAS!

13:38.385 --> 13:40.854
CARMEN, YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BE TAKING A QUIZ.

13:40.854 --> 13:42.422
YOU CAN'T GO
ON THE COMPUTER NOW.

13:42.422 --> 13:44.124
BUT KEVIN JUST SENT ME
A TEXT MESSAGE

13:44.124 --> 13:45.425
AND TOLD ME
TO CHECK MY E-MAIL.

13:45.425 --> 13:48.195
NO, YOU COULD BE LOOKING UP
THE ANSWERS.

13:48.195 --> 13:49.296
WHAT?

13:49.296 --> 13:52.565
YOU'RE ACCUSING ME
OF CHEATING NOW?

13:52.565 --> 13:53.700
YOU KNOW WHAT?

13:53.700 --> 13:54.935
THIS IS HELL!

13:54.935 --> 13:56.469
I CAN'T TAKE
THIS ANYMORE!

13:56.469 --> 13:58.671
THERE'S NO BREAKS,
THERE'S NO ONE TO TALK TO.

13:58.671 --> 14:00.107
IT'S JUST YOU ALL DAY!

14:00.107 --> 14:03.410
HAVE YOU EVER SPENT
EIGHT HOURS WITH YOURSELF?

14:03.410 --> 14:07.214
NO WONDER DAD
HIDES IN THE GARAGE.

14:10.217 --> 14:12.852
YEAH, I GO OUT THERE
TO BUILD THINGS.

14:12.852 --> 14:15.655
IT DOESN'T TAKE THREE YEARS
TO BUILD A BIRDHOUSE.

14:15.655 --> 14:19.626
IT DOES IF YOU'RE DOING IT
SOUTHERN-PLANTATION STYLE.

14:19.626 --> 14:23.696
CARMEN, I'M BEING TOUGH ON YOU
FOR YOUR OWN GOOD.

14:23.696 --> 14:24.998
OH, NO, YOU'RE NOT.

14:24.998 --> 14:26.499
THIS ISN'T EVEN
ABOUT ME.

14:26.499 --> 14:28.902
YOU'VE GOT NO JOB,
NO WEDDING TO PLAN ANYMORE.

14:28.902 --> 14:30.270
DAD WAS RIGHT.

14:30.270 --> 14:32.405
YOU'VE GOT NOTHING ELSE
IN YOUR LIFE.

14:33.873 --> 14:36.109
ANGIE, THAT'S
NOT EXACTLY WHAT I SAID.

14:37.244 --> 14:39.346
ANGIE!

14:42.715 --> 14:45.152
YOU JUST HURT THE ONE PERSON
WILLING TO GIVE UP HER TIME

14:45.152 --> 14:46.653
TO HELP YOU MAKE
SOMETHING OF YOUR LIFE.

14:46.653 --> 14:48.321
BUT SHE --
I DON'T WANT
TO HEAR IT.

14:48.321 --> 14:50.590
I WANT YOU TO GO TO THE GARAGE
AND BUILD ME A BIRDHOUSE

14:50.590 --> 14:53.660
THAT LOOKS LIKE
IT TOOK ME THREE YEARS.

15:02.035 --> 15:04.037
YOU OKAY TO TALK NOW?

15:04.037 --> 15:06.506
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING OUT HERE?

15:06.506 --> 15:08.942
SAME THING I'VE DONE
WITH MY LIFE --

15:08.942 --> 15:10.410
NOTHING.

15:12.145 --> 15:13.846
ACTUALLY, THAT'S NOT TRUE.

15:13.846 --> 15:16.950
I'M OXIDIZING MY CELLS.

15:16.950 --> 15:20.988
ACCORDING TO CARMEN'S BIOLOGY
BOOK, EVERY BREATH I TAKE,

15:20.988 --> 15:23.190
I'M CREATING FREE RADICALS
IN MY SYSTEM

15:23.190 --> 15:25.658
THAT WILL SLOWLY KILL ME.

15:25.658 --> 15:27.494
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

15:29.329 --> 15:32.332
THERE, A LITTLE CLOSER.

15:32.332 --> 15:34.167
LOOK, ANGIE,
I WANT TO APOLOGIZE.

15:34.167 --> 15:36.403
I NEVER SAID YOU HAD NOTHING
GOING ON IN YOUR LIFE.

15:36.403 --> 15:38.105
CARMEN TWISTED
MY WORDS AROUND.

15:38.105 --> 15:40.707
DON'T APOLOGIZE.
SHE'S RIGHT.

15:40.707 --> 15:42.809
I GOT NOTHING...

15:42.809 --> 15:47.680
NO JOB, HALF-PLANNED WEDDING,
MY KIDS BARELY NEED ME.

15:47.680 --> 15:50.117
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

15:51.985 --> 15:55.188
I CAN'T EVEN HOMESCHOOL
OUR DAUGHTER.

15:55.188 --> 15:57.190
BUT THAT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

15:57.190 --> 15:59.659
PROFESSIONAL TEACHERS
COULDN'T REACH CARMEN.

15:59.659 --> 16:01.995
THEY'RE THINKING
ABOUT CHANGING THE SLOGAN

16:01.995 --> 16:06.399
FROM "NO CHILD GETS LEFT BEHIND"
TO "SHE'S NOT LOOKING, RUN!"

16:10.603 --> 16:12.972
WELL, WE BETTER FIND
SOME OTHER WAY

16:12.972 --> 16:14.941
'CAUSE IF I KEEP
TEACHING CARMEN,

16:14.941 --> 16:16.876
IT'S GONNA RUIN
OUR RELATIONSHIP.

16:16.876 --> 16:20.413
OUR DAUGHTER'S
A MOODY, EMOTIONAL BRAT.

16:20.413 --> 16:23.483
I NEVER THOUGHT I WOULD
ACTUALLY HEAR YOU SAY THAT.

16:23.483 --> 16:25.418
NOW WE'RE ON THE SAME PAGE.

16:25.418 --> 16:28.155
BUT YOU STILL HAVE FAITH
IN THE BOY, THOUGH, RIGHT?

16:28.155 --> 16:29.289
OF COURSE I DO.

16:29.289 --> 16:32.125
YEAH, ME TOO.
VERY TALENTED.

16:33.726 --> 16:36.896
BUT THIS STARTED
WAY BEFORE CARMEN.

16:36.896 --> 16:41.201
LOOK AT ALL THE GREAT STUFF
I DID IN HIGH SCHOOL --

16:41.201 --> 16:45.738
HONOR ROLL,
NATIONAL MERIT SCHOLAR...

16:47.540 --> 16:50.310
...PRESIDENT
OF THE FRENCH CLUB.

16:50.310 --> 16:52.679
BOY, ANGIE,
WHEN YOU MARRIED ME,

16:52.679 --> 16:56.749
YOU GOT ON THAT ELEVATOR AND
YOU PRESSED DOWN, DIDN'T YOU?

16:56.749 --> 16:58.251
NO, shh!

16:58.251 --> 17:00.620
DON'T YOU EVER SAY THAT.

17:00.620 --> 17:03.756
I DON'T REGRET MARRYING YOU
AND HAVING A FAMILY.

17:03.756 --> 17:05.625
I REGRET WHAT I DIDN'T DO.

17:05.625 --> 17:09.962
I COULD HAVE GONE TO COLLEGE
AND GOTTEN MY MBA.

17:09.962 --> 17:12.199
I REMEMBER TALKING
IN HIGH SCHOOL

17:12.199 --> 17:14.401
LIKE I WAS GONNA TAKE
THE WORLD BY STORM --

17:14.401 --> 17:17.837
OWN MY OWN BUSINESS,
BECOME A MILLIONAIRE.

17:17.837 --> 17:21.241
YOU'RE GONNA BEAT YOURSELF UP
ABOUT THIS AGAIN?

17:21.241 --> 17:22.509
LOOK, ANGIE, AT THE TIME,

17:22.509 --> 17:25.412
BOTTLED WATER
SEEMED LIKE A STUPID IDEA.

17:31.151 --> 17:32.819
DAD, WHERE'S MOM?

17:32.819 --> 17:34.487
SHE'S STILL SLEEPING.

17:34.487 --> 17:36.323
HEY, CARMEN...

17:36.323 --> 17:38.791
THERE'S SOMETHING
THAT WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT.

17:38.791 --> 17:41.128
I KNOW.

17:41.128 --> 17:43.029
I WANT TO APOLOGIZE.

17:43.029 --> 17:44.664
I'VE GOT
TO CHANGE MY ATTITUDE.

17:44.664 --> 17:47.267
I'VE GOT TO WORK HARDER,
AND I'VE GOT TO PAY ATTENTION.

17:47.267 --> 17:49.669
GOOD, MAYBE THAT'LL KEEP
THE NUNS FROM BEATING YOU

17:49.669 --> 17:51.538
LIKE A TOM-TOM
AT CATHOLIC SCHOOL.

17:51.538 --> 17:54.307
NO, DAD,
PLEASE DON'T MAKE ME GO.

17:54.307 --> 17:55.808
I CAN'T GO TO CATHOLIC --
MOM!

17:55.808 --> 17:58.311
MOM, I PROMISE I'LL
NEVER DO ANYTHING AGAIN.

17:58.311 --> 18:00.147
JUST PLEASE DON'T MAKE ME GO.

18:00.147 --> 18:01.181
SORRY.

18:01.181 --> 18:02.782
THAT'S RIGHT.

18:02.782 --> 18:05.352
GOD'S YOUR NEW PRINCIPAL.

18:08.188 --> 18:11.090
AND I WOULDN'T MOUTH OFF
TO HIM.

18:11.090 --> 18:12.825
THE ISRAELITES --

18:12.825 --> 18:15.228
THEY WERE WANDERING
THE DESERT FOR 40 YEARS.

18:15.228 --> 18:17.597
THAT WAS DETENTION.

18:22.068 --> 18:24.204
HONEY, COME WITH ME.

18:24.204 --> 18:26.673
I WANT YOU TO SEE THIS.

18:30.109 --> 18:32.078
WHY ARE WE GOING
TO THE GARAGE?

18:32.078 --> 18:34.013
WE'RE NOT GOING
TO THE GARAGE.

18:34.013 --> 18:37.016
WE ARE GOING TO...

18:37.016 --> 18:40.787
YOUR NEW HOME OFFICE!

18:43.122 --> 18:47.394
GEORGE, I LOVE
THAT YOU DID THIS FOR ME.

18:47.394 --> 18:49.262
ANGE,
IT'S NOT DONE YET.

18:49.262 --> 18:51.431
BUT WHEN I'M FINISHED,
IT'S GONNA BE AMAZING.

18:51.431 --> 18:54.301
NOW ALL YOU HAVE TO DO
IS DECIDE ON A CAREER.

18:54.301 --> 18:56.403
ANGIE LOPEZ...

18:56.403 --> 19:00.473
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO BE
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE?

19:02.809 --> 19:04.677
I DON'T KNOW.

19:04.677 --> 19:06.546
OH, HEY,
YOUR PHONE'S RINGING.

19:06.546 --> 19:08.315
ANGIE LOPEZ'S OFFICE.

19:08.315 --> 19:09.882
YEAH, SHE'S HERE.

19:09.882 --> 19:11.218
AND SHE'D LOVE TO HELP YOU

19:11.218 --> 19:13.620
BECAUSE SHE'S
IN THE BUSINESS OF...

19:13.620 --> 19:16.623
[ STAMMERS ]

19:16.623 --> 19:18.258
HOLD, PLEASE.

19:18.258 --> 19:19.692
OH, LOOK, ANGIE.
LINE TWO.

19:19.692 --> 19:22.329
ANGIE LOPEZ.
HOLD, PLEASE. OH, MY GOD.

19:22.329 --> 19:23.396
ANGIE LOPEZ.
HOLD, PLEASE.

19:23.396 --> 19:25.064
YEAH, SHE'S HERE.

19:25.064 --> 19:28.535
AND SHE'D LOVE TO HELP YOU WITH
HER INCREDIBLE SUPPLY OF...

19:31.638 --> 19:32.939
SERVICE OF...

19:34.941 --> 19:36.643
HAND-DIPPED?

19:36.643 --> 19:41.781
HONEY, I LOVE THAT YOU DID
ALL OF THIS FOR ME.

19:41.781 --> 19:44.317
I JUST -- I JUST NEED
SOME TIME TO THINK.

19:44.317 --> 19:46.085
ANGIE, DON'T THINK.
GO WITH YOUR GUT.

19:46.085 --> 19:48.288
WHAT'S THE FIRST THING
THAT COMES INTO YOUR HEAD?

19:48.288 --> 19:50.390
OH, GOD, NO,
THE WEDDING --

19:50.390 --> 19:53.726
I FORGOT TO CALL THE FLORIST
AND CANCEL THE CALLA LILIES.

19:53.726 --> 19:55.995
FORGET ABOUT
ALL THAT WEDDING CRAP.

19:55.995 --> 19:57.464
IN THE SCHEME OF LIFE,

19:57.464 --> 19:59.766
WEDDING DETAILS
MEAN ABSOLUTELY NOTHING.

19:59.766 --> 20:01.200
I HATE THEM!

20:01.200 --> 20:03.636
I GOT IT.

20:03.636 --> 20:05.472
I WANT TO BE
A WEDDING PLANNER.

20:05.472 --> 20:08.140
I'LL SUPPORT YOU 100%.

20:08.140 --> 20:10.243
NO, NO.

20:10.243 --> 20:12.879
I MEAN IT.
I MEAN, I'M REALLY GOOD AT IT.

20:12.879 --> 20:16.516
I HAVE A MIND FOR DETAILS.
I LOVE ORGANIZING THINGS.

20:16.516 --> 20:19.218
I COULD DO THIS.

20:19.218 --> 20:21.988
THEN, BABY, DO IT.
ALL RIGHT?

20:21.988 --> 20:23.423
JUST PROMISE ME ONE THING.

20:23.423 --> 20:25.925
WHEN YOUR BUSINESS TAKES OFF
AND YOU MAKE IT,

20:25.925 --> 20:27.226
THAT I CAN QUIT WORK

20:27.226 --> 20:30.563
AND LOUNGE AROUND THE HOUSE
IN MY SWEATS ALL DAY.

20:30.563 --> 20:33.466
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK
I WAS DOING?

20:41.641 --> 20:43.743
HEY, DAD.
WANNA PLAY CATCH?

20:44.043 --> 20:45.312
LATER.

20:45.312 --> 20:46.446
LATER, WHEN?

20:46.446 --> 20:49.516
I DON'T KNOW.
LATER, LATER.

20:49.516 --> 20:51.250
I'M NOT 6 ANYMORE.

20:51.250 --> 20:53.620
I KNOW THAT "LATER, LATER"
MEANS NEVER.

20:53.620 --> 20:57.624
GOOD BOY.
WHY DON'T YOU GO...COLOR?

20:57.624 --> 20:58.625
FINE.

21:13.340 --> 21:15.342
YOU READY
FOR SOME FOOTBALL, MAX?

21:15.342 --> 21:16.409
YEAH!

21:16.409 --> 21:17.744
GOOD BOY, GO DEEP!

21:17.744 --> 21:19.011
WA-CHA!
